            </p>
            <button>Explore</button>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- quote section -->

    <div class="stories">
      <h2>Real stories</h2>
      <div class="story-box">
        <div class="quotes" data-aos="zoom-in-up">
          <div><i class="fas fa-quote-left"></i></div>
          <div>
            I love this Vitamin C serum, I can see my skin becomes brighter
